The '''Palm App Catalog''' is an [[online marketplace]] for applications for [[Palm, Inc.|Palm]] mobile devices running [[webOS]] but not [[Palm OS]].
The App Catalog is similar to [[Apple Inc.|Apple]]'s [[App Store (iOS)|App Store]] for [[iOS (Apple)|iOS]], [[Google]]'s [[Android Market]] for [[Android (operating system)|Android]], and [[Nokia]]'s [[Ovi (Nokia)#Ovi Store|Ovi Store]] for Nokia devices. At the time of the Palm Pre launch, the App Catalog featured 18 applications.{{citation needed|date=August 2009}}
